<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像現在這樣子，<delay20 />
有朋友來我家裡玩的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總是會覺得很緊張呢～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />待在房間的時候，更要記得磨練自己！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前看的雜誌上<delay20 />是這麼寫的唷～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我就馬上跑去買<delay8 />
打磨用的刷子跟布了，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下來該怎麼做呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拜託你不要到處亂看喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果被你看到零食的屑屑掉在房間裡的話，<delay20 />
那不是很害羞嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在老家的時候呀，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />房間裡面<delay20 />
其實裡面還滿亂的唷～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過開始一個人生活以後，<delay20 />
不就得自己打理所有事情嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我就變得很會整理房間了喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說每次碰到有人在發面紙，<delay20 />
我啊，<delay20 />總是沒辦法拒絕對方……<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果家裡的面紙就越積越多了啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到你們兩個
會同時來我房間玩，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得<delay20 />今天真有趣耶～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你們就把這裡當自己家吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我真沒想到你們兩個會同時來我家，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還滿稀奇的呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你能趁這個機會，<delay20 />
和<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />
變得更親近的話就好了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天好熱鬧，我也玩得超開心的～！<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等大家都回去以後，<delay20 />如果我覺得寂寞的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就來大聲唱唱歌好了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得有大家過來玩，<delay20 />
我房間裡的氣氛<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也變得比平常更High了呢～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很喜歡<delay20 />跟大家在一起熱鬧地玩耍，<delay20 />
這樣真的好開心唷～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>